com.github.wuic.util
Class AbstractBuilderFactory<T extends GenericBuilder>

java.lang.Object
  com.github.wuic.util.AbstractBuilderFactory<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
EngineBuilderFactory, NutDaoBuilderFactory, NutFilterBuilderFactory
public abstract class AbstractBuilderFactory<T extends GenericBuilder>
extends Object

This factory discovers automatically both embedded and extension sets of GenericBuilder implementations by checking if they are in classpath or not.

Once the factory is instantiated, it is able to create a GenericBuilder thanks to the simple name (class name without package) of the implementation. Two classes with the same name but in two different packages can't be managed.
